Package io.tessilab.oss.openutils.locker

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DAO
    The class than a Data Acess Object of a JobLocker must implement
    JobParameter
    The interface that a parameter locked by JobLocker must implement.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAOResponse
    The class to encapsulate the answer of a DAO
    ElasticSearchDAO
    The concrete DAO to write in a ElasticSearch database.
    JobLocker<JOBTYPE extends JobParameter>
    The class that use a DAO to lock jobs, in for example a parallel context execution.
    StringJobParameter
    The simpliest job parameter that has only a string create when the object is instancieted.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JobLockerError
    The class throw when there is bad use of the JobLocker
